{"tid":1893652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國提升對日韓旅遊警示至第二級","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T11:54:50.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d6b0a8b85b73d969e8f3c8831b8b53c55aae38","tid":1893652,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"日本和南韓的新型肺炎確診病例近日快速增加，美國國務院與疾控中心提升對日韓旅遊警示至第二級。<br />\n<br />\n國務院呼籲前往兩地的美國國民提高警惕。疾控中心則表示，日韓兩國的新型冠狀病毒透過不明途徑出現人傳人情況，呼籲長者與慢性病患者考慮如非必要，推遲前往兩地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510228-20200223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510228-20200223.htm&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=e09534ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510228-20200223.htm&h=b0ebf89b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510228-20200223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"19de6a7e14a8d9103a98ebb63bcb948cd843778e","tid":1893652,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"日韓都係抵撚死架啦，原本可以隔岸觀火食花生變左深受其害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}